            <description><![CDATA[【夏天这种虫子千万别拍！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%9A%90%E7%BF%85%E8%99%AB%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%92%E6%B6%B2%E5%A0%AA%E6%AF%94%E7%A1%AB%E9%85%B8%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%9A%90%E7%BF%85%E8%99%AB%E7%9A%84%E6%AF%92%E6%B6%B2%E5%A0%AA%E6%AF%94%E7%A1%AB%E9%85%B8%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#隐翅虫的毒液堪比硫酸#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[衰]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_shuai-285d2d97c7.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E8%84%B8%E8%A2%AB%E9%9A%90%E7%BF%85%E8%99%AB%E6%AF%81%E5%AE%B9%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E8%84%B8%E8%A2%AB%E9%9A%90%E7%BF%85%E8%99%AB%E6%AF%81%E5%AE%B9%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#我的脸被隐翅虫毁容了#</span></a> 近期，因接触隐翅虫导致严重皮炎的患者不在少数。专家提醒，隐翅虫主要分布于灌丛草地等环境，它本身没有攻击性，只要不去拍打它，防止它的毒液接触我们的皮肤，就可以避免被它伤害。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4781640334114898" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视频的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.0.0.1383.769/007S2YvRly1h3c4xai095j312f0lkwg9.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/dn5NJHBUlx07WW5pApss01041200FyEm0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1